                            <comment id="14717449" author="tjake" created="Thu, 27 Aug 2015 20:21:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/tjake/cassandra/tree/10164&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/tjake-10164-testall/1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;tests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/tjake-10164-dtest/1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;dtests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;I cleaned up the areas that were trying to catch write timeouts from submitMV since that isn&apos;t possible as it&apos;s all done locally now and actual view updates are async.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Added logic to make MV updates from CL replay not write to the commit log (since we always flush after CL replay anyway)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Added logic to avoid CL when updating mutations from a streamed sstable (it will flush before transaction is complete)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Found/Fixed a little bug in the builder that would not build &amp;gt; 128 rows in a partition.  I&apos;ll add a test for this...&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
